#       ‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚¢Ä‚°†‚†∂‚†ã‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä
#  üêû Auto lanzamiento y guardado autom√°tico de proyectos Burp
# =============================================================


BURP_CMD="burpsuite"
SCRIPT_DIR="$HOME/.config/bspwm/scripts"
USER_CONF="$SCRIPT_DIR/conf.json"
ICON_OK="üü¢"
ICON_ERR="üî¥"

# Verificar si conf.json existe
if [[ ! -f "$USER_CONF" ]]; then
    notify-send "BurpSuite" "$ICON_ERR No se encontr√≥ conf.json en:\n$USER_CONF"
    exit 1
fi

# Mostrar notificaci√≥n de inicio
notify-send "BurpSuite" "‚è≥ Iniciando BurpSuite..."

# Ejecutar Burp con la configuraci√≥n
if "$BURP_CMD" --config "$USER_CONF" & disown; then
    notify-send "BurpSuite" "$ICON_OK BurpSuite iniciado correctamente con conf.json"
else
    notify-send "BurpSuite" "$ICON_ERR Error al lanzar BurpSuite"
    exit 1
fi
